transcripts: Hi I'm Lori Greiner an inventor and entrepreneur and a shark on ABC Shark Tank. I'm known for creating products that make your live's easier. I created over 400 products and my jewelry and cosmetic organizers are a big favorite of women all over. I'm so excited to be at Bed Bath and Beyond so that they can share them with you. I've designed each of them so that you can see everything at a quick glance. Forget about the days of rummaging through piles of makeup for Tangled jewelry. the jewelry box opens and swivels on each level so that you can see all of your jewelry. I have specially designated compartments for your rings, pins, all your jewelry pieces. The earring stands slide so you can see everything at a glance and there's an anti tarnish lining that will keep your silver tarnish free for 25 years or more and when you're done with making your selection, it just all swivels close and what are you left with? A beautiful jewelry box. My patented designs allow to store and see hundreds of pieces instantly. Look for an assortment of my cosmetic and jewelry organizers at select Bed Bath & Beyond stores and online
